<p>This simple but clever idea comes form <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20090101215451/http://blog.xna3.com/2007/12/2d-deformable-level.html" rel="nofollow">this fantastic article</a>. I simply changed things to suit my game. I tried to make the code as clean and simple as I could, which is not easy when iterating through multiple for loops.</p>
